OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,FThe MP for Makerfield has officially
OL,7,Fstood down, paving the way for Andy
OL,8,FBurnham's bid to return to Westminster.
OL,10,FJosh Simons was elected to the role in
OL,11,F2024 General Election, but has now
OL,12,Fofficially vacated the Commons and
OL,13,Fendorsed the Mayor of Greater
OL,14,FManchester to take his place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
