CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779113476
OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,FThere is no formal procedure for
OL,7,Fstanding down as an MP, and so instead
OL,8,FMr Simons has been named the Bailiff
OL,9,Fof the Three Hundreds of Chiltern; an
OL,10,Farchaic and ceremonial role that
OL,11,Fcannot be held while also serving as a
OL,12,FMember of Parliament.
OL,14,FApplications for Labour's Makerfield
OL,15,Fcandidacy close on Monday, with Andy
OL,16,FBurnham currently being the only
OL,17,Fperson to put themselves forward to
OL,18,Frepresent his party.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
