OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779113476
OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,FThe party's ruling National Executive
OL,7,FCommittee will endorse a candidate on
OL,8,FThursday 21 May.
OL,10,FThe former Cabinet Office minister
OL,11,Frejected suggestions he had been
OL,12,Fplotting Mr Burnham's return to
OL,13,FParliament for some time, insisting he
OL,14,Fand the mayor simply discussed
OL,15,Fpolitics over a pint.
OL,17,FMr Simons said he made the decision
OL,18,Fafter discussing it with his wife
OL,19,Ffollowing the local election results.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
