OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779113476
OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,FHe said: "It's been incredibly fast
OL,7,Ffor me... It wasn't just me, it was my
OL,8,Fwife. We did this as a family, because
OL,9,Fit's about the sacrifices on behalf of
OL,10,Fthe family.
OL,12,F"For me, it wasn't about... people
OL,13,Falways ask (about) cutting deals, are
OL,14,Fyou going to run for mayor, are you
OL,15,Fgoing to be in the Lords? No, no, no.
OL,17,F"It was about, 'what does Andy think
OL,18,Fthat he's going to do to the Labour
OL,19,FParty and to the country if he wins
OL,20,Fthis by-election?', and that's what
OL,21,Fmatters."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
