PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779113476
OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,FMr Simons said he believes stepping
OL,7,Fdown is in the "best interests" of his
OL,8,Fparty, community and country.
OL,10,FHe said: "I think doing things for
OL,11,Fyour community and your country that
OL,12,Fare very much not in your own personal
OL,13,Freasons is the kind of thing we should
OL,14,Fdo in politics sometimes.
OL,16,F"This has been a really tough decision
OL,17,Ffor me and my family. I have very
OL,18,Fyoung kids, I've got a three-week-old
OL,19,Fbaby.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@_O]rD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779113476
OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,F"This was not an easy thing to do, and
OL,7,FI wouldn't have done it unless I
OL,8,Freally, really believed, at the end of
OL,9,Fthe day, that this was in the best
OL,10,Finterests of the Labour Party, my
OL,11,Fcommunity, and most importantly, the
OL,12,Fcountry."
OL,14,FAsked what Mr Burnham would do
OL,15,Fdifferently to Sir Keir Starmer, Mr
OL,16,FSimons said the mayor is committed to
OL,17,Freducing the cost of energy, water and
OL,18,Fsocial housing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
