PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779113476
OL,3,CJosh Simons officially stands down as
OL,4,CMP
OL,6,F"Those things, that are the basics of
OL,7,Four lives, that we all depend on, have
OL,8,Fgotten so expensive, and one of the
OL,9,Freasons why they've gotten so
OL,10,Fexpensive, not the only, but one of
OL,11,Fthe reasons why they've gotten so
OL,12,Fexpensive, is that we privatise a lot
OL,13,Fof them, and often the bills that we
OL,14,Fpay go to the shareholders," he said.
